          0.6509803921568628,
          0.6278787878787879,
          0.7521568627450981,
          0.6393939393939394
        ],
        "order": 36
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_newspaper_baa51a22898f0d534a6c404ba8f12fb1_1_29",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "It is ordered: 1. The Commission establishes Docket Nos. MC2015-63 and CP2015-94 to consider the matters raised in each docket.",
        "bbox": [
          0.3607843137254902,
          0.6448484848484849,
          0.636078431372549,
          0.7109090909090909
        ],
        "order": 37
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_newspaper_baa51a22898f0d534a6c404ba8f12fb1_1_48",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "In accordance with 39 U.S.C. 3642 and 39 CFR 3020.30 et seq., the Postal Service filed a formal request and associated supporting information to add Priority Mail Contract 128 to the competitive product list.1",
        "bbox": [
          0.6501960784313725,
          0.6448484848484849,
          0.908235294117647,
          0.7193939393939394
        ],
        "order": 38
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_newspaper_baa51a22898f0d534a6c404ba8f12fb1_1_13",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "ADDREssEs: Submit comments electronically via the Commission's Filing Online system at http:// www.prc.gov. Those who cannot submit comments electronically should contact the person identified in the FoR FURTHER INFORMATION CONTACT Section by telephone for advice on filing alternatives.",
        "bbox": [
          0.07215686274509804,
          0.656969696969697,
          0.3458823529411765,
          0.7703030303030303
        ],
        "order": 39
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_newspaper_baa51a22898f0d534a6c404ba8f12fb1_1_30",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "2.Pursuant to 39 U.S.C. 505, Lyudmila Y. Bzhilyanskaya is appointed to serve as an officer of the Commission to represent the interests of the general public in these proceedings (Public Representative).",
        "bbox": [
          0.3615686274509804,
          0.713939393939394,
          0.636078431372549,
          0.7903030303030303
        ],
        "order": 40
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_newspaper_baa51a22898f0d534a6c404ba8f12fb1_1_49",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "The Postal Service contemporaneously filed a redacted contract related to the proposed new product under 39 U.S.C. 3632(b)(3) and 39 CFR 3015.5. Id. Attachment B.",
        "bbox": [
          0.6509803921568628,
          0.7206060606060606,
          0.9192156862745098,
          0.7824242424242425
        ],
        "order": 41
      }
    ]
  },
